'''Advb''' was the official language of [[Riflor/Legends|Riflor]], spoken by the [[Advozse/Legends|Advozsec]]. The language had a written form.<ref name="Ultimate Alien Anthology" />

Written and spoken Advb was the language of choice of most of the Advozsec in [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]], with only a few of them bothering with learning [[Galactic Basic Standard/Legends|Basic]]. Advb was not spoken by any other species, and since the destruction of all the life on Riflor, Advb was at best a lost language.

